{
  "stem": "2522.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The deportation lists were made up by the Judenrat, in other words, the local Kommandatura, which was basically a German skeleton, cruel, only two or three Gestapo officers who were there anyway handed over, well, we want so many Jews, you know, so many cars.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we have-- it was done through production scheduling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the way, one of the most interesting contributions I made to, to the Holocaust Museum was to identify the punch card, the counting machines, IBM machines, that were used to schedule transports.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, in fact, helped the Holocaust Museum to locate an authentic German IBM machine made in 1932, which was identical to the machine that was used for scheduling transports.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Garda handed it over, made sure that the policeman does, does not do anything improper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, the Garda was there particularly to make sure that the property of the Jews who went to-- in a transport immediately gets sequestered and properly acquired because it was a process by which-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a process by which, in fact, the state acquired wealth for distribution to their faithful.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry for the disturbance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we have a bird out there who sounds like a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The deportation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans have a headquarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know where it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hand over a requisition list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here are so many cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fill them with Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here is the quota.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Goes to the Garda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Garda hands it over to the police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The police comes to, to the-- to the Jewish community leaders and says, OK, we need 320.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we need-- and, and they give qualifications.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have to be this-and-this age.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
